B.Sl=new A.f("Largemouth Bass","Micropterus salmoides",B.m,"30\u201360 cm, up to 10 kg","Lakes, ponds, rivers","Freshwater","Fish, frogs, crayfish","Spinnerbaits, crankbaits, plastic worms","The most popular game fish in the USA. Known for aggressive strikes and acrobatic leaps when hooked. Prefers warm, vegetated waters with plenty of cover like logs and lily pads.",B.a0e,B.cf)
