B.Qm=new A.f("Sauger","Sander canadensis",B.m,"25\u201345 cm, up to 3 kg","Large rivers, reservoirs","Freshwater","Small fish, insects","Jigs, spinners, live minnows","A smaller cousin of the walleye with a more slender body. Distinguished by dark saddle marks on the dorsal fin. Prefers large, turbid rivers.",B.YO,B.bM)
